{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回「人面桃花」。纤纤是雷奇峰雷八太爷家中的丫鬟，与雷家大少爷小雷相爱并怀有身孕。雷奇峰六十大寿之夜，小雷故意在桃花林中以冷酷言辞伤害纤纤，逼她离开，实则是为了保护她和腹中骨肉。九幽一窝蜂的仇家在十三年后前来复仇，褐衣人讨回断手，人面桃花蜂现身索命。雷夫人以死相胁逼走仆人，自己却在战斗中中毒身亡。平家三兄弟虽是暗器名家，也在混战中全部罹难。雷奇峰夫妇双双战死，小雷身受重伤倒在血泊中。人面桃花蜂揭开面具，露出脸上被雷奇峰所留的刀疤——原来她的母亲死于雷奇峰刀下，她五岁时便被毁容。小雷最终放走了她。大火将雷家山庄化为焦土，小雷在废墟中苏醒，故事由此展开。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不是人，是块木头。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看看她的胸，岂非也平得像块木头一样，还说她是个美人哩，我若是男人，就绝不要她。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的女人，抱在怀里，也一定好像抱着块木头一样。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "小雷……小雷……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你又在外面打了架……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你体想骗我，你衣服上还有血。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "你记不记得你的血也曾染在我衣服上？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你……你刚才难道有过别的女人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "我难道不能有别的女人？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "可是，你难道竟然忘了，我已经有了你的孩子？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "我怎么知道那是谁的孩子？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "我只知道你是丫头。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_xian_xian",
      "text": "我看你最好还是快走吧！走远些！我还约会了别的人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_xian",
      "speaker_name": "纤纤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "我会走的！你放心，以后我永远不会再见到你！可是我发誓，总有一天你要后悔的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大少爷回来了，大家快敬酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还要喝？是不是一定要喝回本钱才肯走？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷升，开大门，送客。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你是不是想把我的人丢光？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你疯了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你为什么要做这种令我见不得人的事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "因为今天晚上，谁也不能留在这里，每个人都非走不可。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "因为他们已来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你说的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "该来的，迟早总是要来的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "不错，既然要来，就不如还是早点来的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "十三年，整整十三年了，这次他们既然敢来，想必已一定很有把握！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "所以除了我们姓雷的之外，无论谁都不能留在这里，江湖中谁都知道，只要是他们到过的地方，一向寸草不留。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你也得赶快走，他们要找的是我。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你至少也该为雷家留个后。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "雷家已有了后。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "在纤纤那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "可是她……她的人呢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "我已叫她走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "她肯走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你怎么能就这样叫她一个人走？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "我已经叫陶峰在暗中保护她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们若还有人留在这里，我就立刻死在你们面前。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九幽一窝蜂到的地方，一向寸草不留，何况人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "褐衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "褐衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "很好，还我的手来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_he_yi_ren",
      "text": "这只手反正已不再能杀人，你要，就拿去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "褐衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "这只手已没有人再能拿走了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_he_yi_ren",
      "text": "的确没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "褐衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "你不认得我？我却忘不了你，也忘不了十三年前在枫林中那一夜。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "你不是她，你骗不了我。十三年前，她已死了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "不错，十三年前，我已经死了，所以现在我才要你还我的命来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "抱歉，手可以还，命却没法子还的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "那么就用你们一家老小九十七条命来还！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "命可以还你，只不过……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "不过怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "我还要问你一句活。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "十三年前的那天晚上，你们在枫林里究竟做了什么事？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "那当然是见不得人的事，聪明的妻子就算知道，也会装糊涂的，你又何必多问？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "原来你一直在瞒着我，一直在骗我，原来你根本没有杀死她。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "你相信她，还是相信我？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "我只想听真话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "我们三十几年夫妻，到现在你还吃醋。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "八十年的夫妻也一样会吃醋的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "就算你要吃醋，现在也不是时候。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "我不管现在是什么时候，你若还不肯说老实话，我先跟你拼命。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "好，我告诉你，那天晚上……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "追不得！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必追。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan_feng",
      "speaker_name": "鬼眼蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "还我的命来吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "怎么样？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "满天花雨，平家三兄弟，几时做了别人奴才的？倒真是叫人想不到的事。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "text": "雷奇峰，你真是个老狐狸，居然神不知，鬼不觉的，将平家三兄弟买回来藏在家里，我佩服你！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_qi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "雷奇峰",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "人面桃花蜂十三年前已死了，这次来的是假的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雷夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你不能死——你要找到纤纤，她很好……她一定会替我养个好孙子。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_lei_fu_ren",
      "text": "我一定会找到她的，一定会带着我们的孩子回来看你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你居然还没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你的父母全都死了，你活着还有什么意思？不如也死了吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你既然不肯死，就去吧，我找的本不是你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 737
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你是不是要杀我？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "为什么？为你父母复仇？你能为父母复仇，我为什么不能？我若做错了，你岂非也同样错。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "何况，我并没有杀人，我的手还没有染上任何人的血，我母亲却是死在你父亲手上的，我亲眼看到他的刀，割断了我母亲的咽喉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "你亲眼看到？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你想不想看看我的脸？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你知不知道这是谁留给我的？……也是你的父亲，那时我只不过才五岁，有谁想得到'神刀大侠'竟会对一个五岁的孩子，下这种毒手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 785
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "现在你是不是还想杀我？是不是还想替你的父母报仇？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lei",
      "speaker_name": "小雷",
      "listener": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "text": "滚出去，快滚，从此莫要让我再见到你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mian_tao_hua_feng",
      "speaker_name": "人面桃花蜂",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lei",
      "text": "你既然不敢再听，我也不必再说下去，因为再说下去，我也会觉得恶心。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 801
    }
  ],
